data.description:
GALA MODEL-Sun City Festival! Immerse yourself in an array of activities and social events in this Premier 55+ Active Adult community offering Resort-Style living. From Copper Canyon Golf Club courses, 16 pickleball courts and fitness centers to clubs and classes; always something exciting happening!
You'll be greeted by a Paved Courtyard as you enter this spacious Open Floor Plan 2Bedroom 2Bathroom + Den which is ideal for an Office/Hobbies.
The KICHEN features staggered Cherry cabinets with Pull out shelving, Gas stove, Large Pantry, Granite Counters, SS Appliances & a Huge Island w/seating.  Primary Suite w/ Bay Window opens to spacious Bathroom with dual sinks & large walk-in closet. 2nd bedroom is perfect for guests. Leased solar with extensive savings, Water softener, 2 car garage + golf cart bay and a ton of cabinet space/workshop in the garage.  Enjoy Arizona entertaining with Built in BBQ, Gas Firepit and above Ground Spa in this Low maintenance private, walled backyard. Pride of ownership. Call this place HOME!
